hopobject.body: Nice to meet you westside pharmacy dothan alabama ** Spanish builder Sacyr said its board haddecided to sell its property division Vallehermoso, a move thatcould help it shed more than 1.2 billion euros ($1.62 billion)of debt. In a note to the stock exchange regulator, Sacyr saidit had received interest in Vallehermoso but that no deal hadyet been finalised. It did not give further details on price orpotential buyers.
